      "rawType": "FX",
      "required": false,
      "helpText": "Enter the static, unchanging part of an open global reference for either a global or a cross-reference that contains the list of record numbers to sort through on the first pass.  The leading up-arrow can be omitted.   For example:  DIZ(662001,\"A\", or TMP(\"NMSP\",$J, ",
