      "dataType": "FREE-TEXT",
      "rawType": "F",
      "required": false,
      "helpText": "  If this sort template is compiled, the first characters of the name of that compiled routine will appear on this node.  Compiled sort routines are re-created each time the sort/print runs.  These characters are concatenated with the next available number from the COMPILED ROUTINE file to create the routine name.   If this node is present, a new compiled sort routine will be created during the FileMan sort/print. ",
